WEBVTT

00:00:00.080 --> 00:00:07.439
Well, good evening everybody. Thank you for joining us again tonight.

00:00:07.440 --> 00:00:15.179
I got this today that will get rid of every fly. Somebody sent this to me; I thought that was the coolest thing ever.

00:00:15.180 --> 00:00:20.409
I told Diana I said, "Guess what? I'm the Terminator."So, we're going to go after the flies today.

00:00:20.410 --> 00:00:28.359
If there's a fly, he's dead. So, I'm excited about it. I loaded it with the salt from the Himalaya and Himalayan salt crystals.

00:00:28.360 --> 00:00:33.739
I can see it go, and so it's fun to play with. I've been shooting at flies all the time.

00:00:33.740 --> 00:00:39.039
You know, I shot myself with it; it stings really bad. But I thought, yeah, that was fun.

00:00:39.040 --> 00:00:42.683
So, whoever sent that, I appreciate that. That was kind of you.

00:00:42.684 --> 00:00:46.738
So, we don't have fly problems no more. In fact, I've been looking for flies.

00:00:46.739 --> 00:00:54.499
I said, leave the door open. Leave the door open. Let's do this.

00:00:54.500 --> 00:01:04.238
All right. Well, last night was different. You know, I've prayed about that all day today.

00:01:04.239 --> 00:01:08.959
What I saw about the person in the boat, Diana and I, we discussed it.

00:01:08.960 --> 00:01:16.558
We had to run errands and do some things, and I told her, we were talking, she went through all the visions and things the Lord has been showing me.

00:01:16.559 --> 00:01:20.639
She asked me about certain things today. It was interesting because Diana doesn't usually ever do that.

00:01:20.640 --> 00:01:40.478
But she said, "As Joseph saw seven fat cows and seven skinny cows, did it have anything to do with a cow?"The cow represented seven plentiful years and seven bad years.

00:01:40.479 --> 00:01:53.499
It was the Lord talking about two shmita cycles. It started with two shmita cycles, two seven-year periods.

00:01:53.500 --> 00:01:56.719
That's the point I say, because I was the reason why I brought it up.

00:01:56.720 --> 00:02:04.879
I've been thinking and meditating on the visions the Lord shows me, that I saw a girl in a boat and she was in the Caribbean.

00:02:04.880 --> 00:02:13.439
It was a white woman and she was on a boat that the sail was messed up and she was sailing for fun.

00:02:13.440 --> 00:02:21.119
I could see her last night bobbing up and down in the water as a storm on the sea was happening.

00:02:21.120 --> 00:02:47.459
She was bobbing up and down and she was crying and she was sitting on the deck of this white boat and it was moving up and down; she was sobbing because she had no way of communicating to people to tell them that she was in distress and she was too far out for the Coast Guard to hear her or for them to be watching for her.

00:02:47.460 --> 00:02:58.799
She was too far out. But she came from Florida. There was something about her in the Caribbean that she got into; something happened and I was interceding for this.

00:02:58.800 --> 00:03:11.759
I was thinking is this a metaphor? As I was praying into that, I was seeing people behind their computers last night and they were saying, "Does God really care about me?

00:03:11.760 --> 00:03:25.532
I feel all alone. I have no family. I come, I work 8 to 5, I'm by myself all the time,"and they were thinking about harming themselves physically.

00:03:25.533 --> 00:03:33.999
They were feeling that they were completely lost. Does God really care about me?

00:03:34.000 --> 00:03:42.318
Does God really understand that I'm hurting right now? Does he even care that I am?

00:03:42.319 --> 00:03:53.359
And as I was praying, I could feel the hopelessness of these individuals last night, that they felt like there was no hope for their life.

00:03:53.360 --> 00:04:05.327
There was such a depression and such a sense of not self-worth, so inadequate. It was so heavy.

00:04:05.328 --> 00:04:12.399
And as I was praying, I saw a cork bobbing down in the water and then it became a person.

00:04:12.400 --> 00:04:27.770
And as they began to sink into the water and the water was about to take their last breath in their life, they would shoot up to the top and they would get just enough air just to sustain them to keep their body alive.

00:04:27.771 --> 00:04:34.947
Almost like the bread of affliction. And I could see them dropping back down and trying to fight to come up to the air again.

00:04:34.948 --> 00:04:40.638
And they were fighting for everything they had to have just one more breath of air.

00:04:40.639 --> 00:04:48.079
And that's the way they were living. If I could just get one more breath of air.

00:04:48.080 --> 00:04:58.959
And they go, [gasps] and they go back down. And it was very heavy. As I'm saying this, it's heavy.

00:04:58.960 --> 00:05:13.519
But I went over the visions and I thought, is this girl in the ocean, is this a type of shadow of where people are spiritually, of where they are with their relationship with the Lord?

00:05:13.520 --> 00:05:21.359
That God is wanting you to come out of the barely getting by, the survival stage, and come into thriving.

00:05:21.360 --> 00:05:26.502
He wants you to thrive the rest. He wants you to be the head and not the tail.

00:05:26.503 --> 00:05:33.930
Above and not beneath. Go through and not go under. To have that relationship with him that you say, "Hello, Father.

00:05:33.931 --> 00:05:41.758
How are you doing today?"That you become intimate with God.

00:05:41.759 --> 00:05:50.159
When you get real with God, I say it all the time. When you get real with God, God will become real to you. Stop being fake.

00:05:50.160 --> 00:06:00.518
I went over all the major ministries, all the people that I've talked to on the phone that I used to dream to talk to, and you realize how human they truly are.

00:06:00.519 --> 00:06:14.879
That they are just a vessel that said yes, just like me. And how I have strategically done everything the Lord has told me to do to get to where I'm at right now and where he tells me I'm going.

00:06:14.880 --> 00:06:22.079
And how I don't ever want the pressure of this to ever choke out the relationship that I have with him.

00:06:22.080 --> 00:06:29.244
It's more valuable than anything else. It's like I told one minister, I don't care about the White House.

00:06:29.245 --> 00:06:33.839
I don't care about certain stuff. In fact, I think it's a joke.

00:06:33.840 --> 00:06:40.689
I talk to the King of Kings and I see angels. They come and visit. That's the thing to me.

00:06:40.690 --> 00:06:46.559
Sitting at the dryer and losing yourself with prayer, and that's what I did.

00:06:46.560 --> 00:06:51.679
Folding laundry, helping Diana, doing things like that, seeking him and finding him.

00:06:51.680 --> 00:07:03.450
All this other—I want to call it crap. Sorry, but it is, the spiritual stuff, all the requests, all that, it's crap.

00:07:03.451 --> 00:07:09.071
It's a distraction. I talked to people across this camera because the Lord told me to.

00:07:09.072 --> 00:07:13.221
But I thought about it a lot today. I thought about the pressure of ministry.

00:07:13.222 --> 00:07:25.159
I have some ministers, I talk to them. They got 40 and 50 staff, 250 staff. They got huge overhead. They got huge bills, huge.

00:07:25.160 --> 00:07:29.839
And if they don't have a certain amount of money come in through their ministry, they're in trouble.

00:07:29.840 --> 00:07:38.638
So they push books. They push things. And I'm not criticizing. That's just not where my heart is. I just want to be Brandon.

00:07:38.639 --> 00:07:43.404
I don't want the pressure of all that with having families and being responsible.

00:07:43.405 --> 00:07:49.399
You got to make sure they got their bills paid by your ministry paying their salary and you got all that.

00:07:49.400 --> 00:08:00.835
And I go, "Good Lord."And Diana goes, "Brandon, do you see we can say whatever I want to say?"And they look at me as a wild hair.

00:08:00.836 --> 00:08:10.638
I say what he says, but I have no fear of it. Last night I told you I saw the Colombian president, his buddies in a box being shipped to him.

00:08:10.639 --> 00:08:19.027
And after it was over—Colombia. Colombia, sorry. Thank you, son. Rewind that. Colombia.

00:08:19.028 --> 00:08:24.268
But I saw his buddies in a box and the Lord said, "Anoint your place of the Lord."I saw a witch after him.

00:08:24.269 --> 00:08:30.039
I saw that. But I didn't have no fear saying it. And most people go, "My god, we got the emails. Are you kidding me?

00:08:30.040 --> 00:08:39.759
Do you say all that?"I said, "I have nothing to fear because I have nothing to lose."If we still do our business and do things on the side there, if this gets turned off, I truly mean that.

00:08:39.760 --> 00:08:46.479
I did this all for the Lord. There's nothing behind it other than I am sold out to Jesus.

00:08:46.480 --> 00:08:55.679
And I told them and I think that's probably why a lot of these other ministries, big ministries, they hold me at arms distance because they don't know what I'm going to do.

00:08:55.680 --> 00:09:02.479
And that's the truth. I don't know what I'm going to do. I'm free. I say what he says to say.

00:09:02.480 --> 00:09:12.901
And if there's repercussions behind it, I pay the price for I say, "Lord, this is what you told me to do."If the channel gets turned off, they silenced me last night again.

00:09:12.902 --> 00:09:18.958
Then everybody had to go, 'Hey, we can't hear you anymore.'YouTube got ticked off, and we get these things.

00:09:18.959 --> 00:09:26.559
They say, 'You can't say that,'and they mute me. Hello, YouTube.

00:09:26.560 --> 00:09:32.559
But I'm bold as a lion, and I'll say what He says to say, and I don't care.

00:09:32.560 --> 00:09:52.719
I did the best I could, and I'll stand before Him and say, 'Lord, I gave You everything I got.'And that might mean that Diana goes, 'You have more, you know what, rocks than I've ever seen anybody have in my life.'Honey, I can't believe some of the stuff you say, but I say it because I don't fear you; I fear Him.

00:09:52.720 --> 00:09:57.199
I'm sold out. I was going over the visions and going over things.

00:09:57.200 --> 00:10:04.124
I think, my God, I've said some things on the internet. They blotted me out last night, and I couldn't figure out why.

00:10:04.125 --> 00:10:07.987
Nobody could hear me. They muted me, and they wanted you to leave.

00:10:07.988 --> 00:10:13.431
They didn't want you hearing what I was saying anymore, so you had to refresh it and come back in.

00:10:13.432 --> 00:10:21.918
For a lot of you—that thousand-plus where it all dropped—so it is what it is.

00:10:21.919 --> 00:10:25.342
Everybody lost sound because YouTube didn't like what I said last night.

00:10:25.343 --> 00:10:39.298
And so, am I afraid of that? Not even a little bit. I didn't get myself here; I didn't do any of it. He did it all.

00:10:39.299 --> 00:10:49.188
Everything I have—I lived in an 800-square-foot house for 17 years of my life with cockroaches and meth dealers all around me.

00:10:49.189 --> 00:10:53.245
I've been at the bottom of the barrel, and now the Lord's blessed me.

00:10:53.246 --> 00:11:04.346
I look around and say, 'I've had little, and I'm not moved by any of it.'I lived with nothing, barely scrimping on food stamps.

00:11:04.347 --> 00:11:18.319
You understand, when you are sold out to Him and there's nothing that you've done in your life to take credit for, you are able to be really free, because I was happy then and I'm happy now.

00:11:18.320 --> 00:11:29.930
I love the Lord, but like I said, my biggest thing is always praying with my kids, teaching them how to pray, teaching them how to deep dip in the rivers.

00:11:29.931 --> 00:11:36.965
My biggest thing is to teach Paisley. I see the intercessory prayer gifts on her. The Lord told me she's going to start to see as she's seeing.

00:11:36.966 --> 00:11:45.839
There are things that I don't talk about, but my little girl is walking in the supernatural at ten years old, and she's already starting to see over and she's able to do things.

00:11:45.840 --> 00:11:56.351
And I impart. I lay hands on her and I impart. I teach her how to jump in that river as a child. I do the same with Braden.

00:11:56.352 --> 00:12:01.838
And if Megan were not overcoming, I would do the same for her, but right now she's overcoming.

00:12:01.839 --> 00:12:15.919
I still pray for her all the time, but it's not like I try to say, 'Honey, will you see?'because she wouldn't tell us if she could. I'm sure she does. I'm free tonight.

00:12:15.920 --> 00:12:26.879
As it clicked today while we were going over the visions and what the Lord has done, there are things that the Lord shows me that we've prayed away.

00:12:26.880 --> 00:12:35.936
I know we've stopped things by the Spirit of God, praying for things and interceding for this man in Colombia.

00:12:35.937 --> 00:12:39.278
I said, 'Lord, I haven't had a lot of visions in the last couple of days.

00:12:39.279 --> 00:12:46.947
You haven't shown me what's going on.'He said, 'I told you when I don't show you something to pray over what I've given you.

00:12:46.948 --> 00:12:58.604
I gave you something that you just see—it's amazing—and you just cast it aside and keep marching.'He said, 'It's like going at Christmas time and you're opening up gifts and you go, "Where's the next one?

00:12:58.605 --> 00:13:04.638
Where's the next one?"and you don't realize what you just unwrapped.'What did He give you?

00:13:04.639 --> 00:13:10.619
Well, hold on a minute. You're a child because you're so excited about all the stuff under the tree.

00:13:10.620 --> 00:13:16.932
He keeps giving you all this stuff and you're not looking at what He gave you out of the box.

00:13:16.933 --> 00:13:24.799
You're taking it for granted because you put it aside and forgot that you even opened it because you're looking at what's ahead.

00:13:24.800 --> 00:13:49.439
He said, 'Stop looking at what's underneath the tree and look at what I already gave you to unwrap and what I'm telling you to pray over.'I'm trying to tell you to pray over the man in Colombia because he's going to lose two friends, somebody really close to him with a beard, and you can pray about this.

00:13:49.440 --> 00:13:56.586
I thought, 'Can I stop it? Are there things that You tell me to stop?'because You told me You want revival in Colombia.

00:13:56.587 --> 00:14:01.679
The ultimate thing is there's witchcraft in the nation and the Lord said, 'I'm going to deal with it.

00:14:01.680 --> 00:14:07.838
But not only that, I want a major harvest of souls with my Latinos.

00:14:07.839 --> 00:14:13.599
It's time to bring them in.'I want you to pray over President Trump.

00:14:13.600 --> 00:14:23.270
I gave this to you when I saw Don Jr. being taken out again, and he was no longer here.

00:14:23.271 --> 00:14:29.999
I saw the storm blowing on him, and He said, 'It's your job. You have to pray for his kids.

00:14:30.000 --> 00:14:38.719
Pray for Don Jr. I'm showing you for the fourth time that the man's life is in danger.

00:14:38.720 --> 00:14:46.519
Pray for Don Jr.'The other kids are not prominent in the vision; they're faded.

00:14:46.520 --> 00:14:52.308
Don Jr. is bold and his life is in danger. And the Lord said, 'Pray for him.

00:14:52.309 --> 00:15:13.039
Pray for Don Jr.'So, instead of opening another package—because there's so much more the Lord wants to show us—look at what He has given me and open the gift of a vision, because you don't have control over it; Jesus does. It's a gift.

00:15:13.040 --> 00:16:02.398
You open it up and don't put the gift over here and say, 'Where's my next one?'I stopped and I looked and I said, 'Let's be thankful that He gave us the warning ahead of time to pray over Don Jr., to pray over the man in Colombia, to pray over Cuba, and to pray over President Trump to make it across the finish line, that he finishes strong, that the 25th Amendment does not happen, that the Black judge in the Supreme Court does not die of prostate cancer or heart disease, that he will stay strong, that his life will not be cut off because of cancer of the prostate: Clarence Thomas.'Pray over voices to be accurate.

00:16:02.399 --> 00:16:14.455
Don't criticize; pray for them—the prophetic voices, the ones that truly have a heart after God and are just missing it because they're human.

00:16:14.456 --> 00:16:18.898
Don't go, 'Well, they're false prophets,'and everyone pick on people.

00:16:18.899 --> 00:16:31.691
Instead, just see it and go, 'Listen, is their heart truly pure and after God and they're just off track a little bit?'versus if it's malicious.

00:16:31.692 --> 00:16:40.559
There are some people that are just good people and just need a little fine-tuning. Everybody needs a tuning.

00:16:40.560 --> 00:16:52.205
The rabbit ears get fuzzy sometimes because of the cares of life—like I told you, the responsibility of having fifty staff, 100, or 200 people in your church, and you have all this stuff going on.

00:16:52.206 --> 00:17:02.319
You have all this responsibility, and the antennas get a little crossed up sometimes because you have all the cares of life on top of you and families depending on you.

00:17:02.320 --> 00:17:12.879
So, in the midst of all the cares of life in a huge ministry, from what I'm learning, have a little grace.

00:17:12.880 --> 00:17:17.481
Pray for some folks; they need help. Pray for their finances. Why?

00:17:17.482 --> 00:17:23.632
We're all on the same mission to save that which was lost—to tell people that Jesus Christ is coming.

00:17:23.633 --> 00:17:30.079
And some people just get a little bit weary in well-doing, and they just need some help.

00:17:30.080 --> 00:17:40.056
I would rather reach my hand down to a brother in a ditch and pull him out than throw more dirt on him as I walk by.

00:17:40.057 --> 00:17:48.479
There are so many people—the sister clipboards—who are throwing dirt on people right now, and I don't want to be associated with it.

00:17:48.480 --> 00:17:54.728
I want to just say, 'Listen, you missed it. You messed up. But let's pull you out of the ditch.

00:17:54.729 --> 00:18:01.279
Let's look at what you did to help the Body of Christ in the past.'Did you get people saved?

00:18:01.280 --> 00:18:08.879
How many did you lead to Christ? How many people did you help out of the ditch whenever they were in the ditch?

00:18:08.880 --> 00:18:13.403
But instead, you didn't throw dirt on them. You helped them out and you washed them up.

00:18:13.404 --> 00:18:21.279
You washed their feet. I saw a vision of Jesus washing the disciples'feet.

00:18:21.280 --> 00:18:33.678
And that was something that we have missed as the body of Christ, that we don't do that: the washing of the feet. This is a sign of covenant. This is something more.

00:18:33.679 --> 00:18:46.959
As I saw washing a minister's feet in a vision as I was praying, and I saw the individual, and the Lord said, 'Do you see the washing of the feet?'Jesus was actually washing the feet of this person.

00:18:46.960 --> 00:18:55.598
And they were washing his feet. And the Lord said, 'There's much more to washing of the feet than you realize.

00:18:55.599 --> 00:19:09.439
Not only about humility, but there's more to this that I want you to pray about that your modern culture doesn't get. Washing of the feet.

00:19:09.440 --> 00:19:19.119
Jesus washed their feet.'And the Lord was speaking to me about washing of the feet today—well, actually yesterday, it was last night.

00:19:19.120 --> 00:19:23.999
And I was praying into that washing of the feet. There's more to this.

00:19:24.000 --> 00:19:30.079
And I thought, what is more to washing of the feet? Jesus took Communion and he washed their feet.

00:19:30.080 --> 00:19:40.079
I thought, why? There's more to this. I know in my modern thinking, it's just like, what really is that?

00:19:40.080 --> 00:19:59.519
I mean, I hate to be ignorant, sorry, but I was just like, 'Lord, you can't wash my feet.'But even Peter and them, they were freaking out about it.

00:19:59.520 --> 00:20:09.199
But Jesus humbled himself and he washed their feet, and they washed his feet. It was a covenant. There's something more to it.

00:20:09.200 --> 00:20:13.999
And I'm sure somebody's written some book about it and they feel like they're an expert at it.

00:20:14.000 --> 00:20:21.119
But the Lord said there's a deeper revelation than what you realize.

00:20:21.120 --> 00:20:32.158
And I thought, well, I want to be a student. Show me. I'll wash your feet, Lord.

00:20:32.159 --> 00:20:40.879
I'll wash the minister's feet. There's something about it.

00:20:40.880 --> 00:20:51.519
So, that's where I was at today. I'm just telling you, I think it's easy to be a critic. It's easy to always poke.

00:20:51.520 --> 00:21:12.479
It's easy to always think, 'Well, my life's not that way.'Whenever you realize when I talk, we go over Kathryn Kuhlman's life and her autobiography, reading over her struggles and her trials and how really beautiful a person she was.

00:21:12.480 --> 00:21:18.079
She had issues. We all have issues. But she truly was a beautiful soul.

00:21:18.080 --> 00:21:25.918
She was a beautiful person. And I just want to be more like Jesus.

00:21:25.919 --> 00:21:37.999
And the more I get into ministry and the more I've learned, it pulls you more away from him, the more they draw you to him because of the pressures of things.

00:21:38.000 --> 00:21:44.879
And the more I realized the Lord said, 'What is it you need of, Brandon? What is this that I've shown you?

00:21:44.880 --> 00:21:54.079
I've done it.'And I thought, 'Lord, if it all goes away, you provided everything.

00:21:54.080 --> 00:21:59.918
You gave me all these lights, the camera, the talk. You did it all.

00:21:59.919 --> 00:22:13.031
And I said what you told me to say.'So I don't know. It was interesting today. I don't know if that helps you any, but it helped me.

00:22:13.032 --> 00:22:29.678
And I think for people who are trying really hard to do ministry and you see the Candace Owens, you see the Tuckers, and I told you there's going to be a great criticism coming out of people in the days ahead concerning the Christians, concerning the way we believe.

00:22:29.679 --> 00:22:38.639
There are things that are going to be criticized greatly. And we haven't seen the beginning of persecution that's coming to the church in America.

00:22:38.640 --> 00:22:45.199
There's great persecution coming. And I've seen some very hard things.

00:22:45.200 --> 00:22:51.599
But I know that in the midst of persecution, it brings forth the greater glory.

00:22:51.600 --> 00:22:58.158
The greater the persecution, the greater the glory. Trials bring forth glory.

00:22:58.159 --> 00:23:04.114
The refining brings forth the glory. So, all right. There you go.

00:23:04.115 --> 00:23:15.839
How long was that? Oh, 35 minutes. Okay. Do you want to show them anything in the news?

00:23:15.840 --> 00:23:27.669
I'm trying to break myself of calling you 'babe'. Go ahead. Okay.

00:23:27.670 --> 00:23:31.610
Turkey had a meeting with Poland today. Now, what did we say was going to happen?

00:23:31.611 --> 00:23:39.759
I said the Lord said Turkey would rise up and it would be about Warsaw, Poland, and they'll strike Poland in the days ahead.

00:23:39.760 --> 00:23:47.622
This is interesting. Why did Turkey meet Poland today? They did a prayer for him.

00:23:47.623 --> 00:23:53.685
Yeah, they did a prayer. Well, that's interesting. Is that in Turkey?

00:23:53.686 --> 00:24:02.119
No, this is in Turkey. Wow. That's what Turkey looks like. So Poland came to Turkey.

00:24:02.120 --> 00:24:23.418
Yes. That's interesting. So Turkey's really pretty. That's not what I thought it would look like; I thought it'd be rocky.

00:24:23.419 --> 00:24:35.119
Yeah. The vampire is really stretching out today for sure. Yeah. So, he had him over and they were talking.

00:24:35.120 --> 00:24:43.167
I was trying to recapture and see what they were saying, but there's not very many.

00:24:43.168 --> 00:24:46.531
What was their point? What was the point of going there? I don't know.

00:24:46.532 --> 00:25:03.459
I think it was because Ukraine was trying to strike them. So, they're trying to... yeah. So Ukraine is trying to strike them. Yes.

00:25:03.460 --> 00:25:20.927
I wonder why I saw unconventional weapons of war with Russia concerning that, if Ukraine is upset at Poland. I could miss it, but it's interesting.

00:25:20.928 --> 00:25:29.839
And then he was saying, on his last day, they're saying he authorized a strike on Russia—British involvement on his last day.

00:25:29.840 --> 00:25:39.239
Some people are saying it's coincidence; some people are saying it's not. British Storm Shadow missiles.

00:25:39.240 --> 00:25:47.146
Those Storm Shadow missiles are long-range—they're not ballistic, but they are missiles.

00:25:47.147 --> 00:25:58.479
So did it go into Moscow? I believe so. Oh my gosh. Now, folks, that's something because this is what I said.

00:25:58.480 --> 00:26:02.810
